# A9: build.rs auto-copies the built mdviewer-askpass helper here as
# `mdviewer-askpass-<target-triple>` so Tauri's externalBin resolves at
# codegen time. The artifacts themselves are produced from sources under
# src/bin/, so they shouldn't be checked in.
mdviewer-askpass-*
!.gitkeep
!.gitignore
